164
00:09:27.701 --> 00:09:29.903
Algo sobre mierda de vaca. creo.

165
00:09:31.471 --> 00:09:33.607
Me moquea la nariz. viejo.

166
00:09:33.741 --> 00:09:35.809
[gritos]

167
00:09:36.576 --> 00:09:38.045
[Los gritos continúan]

168
00:09:38.145 --> 00:09:39.446
